Welcome to sc_intNMF’s documentation!

sc_intNMF is a python library for analysis of single cell multiomic data. Example data found at 10x genomics [https://www.10xgenomics.com/products/single-cell-multiome-atac-plus-gene-expression]. It offers a simple and intuitive API.

Note

This project is under development.
